List of commands
# Moderation !ban - Ban a member. !tempban - Ban a member temporally. (max 30 days) !banalts - Ban a member and their alternative accounts. !unban - Unban a member. !kick - Kick a member. !mute - Mute a member. (chat & voice) !unmute - Unmute a member. !warn - Add/Remove user warnings. !role - Edit a user's roles. !purge - Purge messages. (max 1000) !nuke - Purge all messages in a channel. !verification - Toggle reCAPTCHA verification. (Anti-Raid) !reverify - Force a member (or all members) to re-verify themselves. !autorole - Configure auto-role. (It assigns new members a role) !nick - Edit a user's nickname !slowmode - Toggle slow-mode. # Antispam !blacklist - Edit the word blacklist used for chat filter. !whitelist - Edit the word whitelist used for chat filter. !imagefilter - Toggle image filter. # Backup !backup - Create a server backup. (channels, roles and server settings) !restore - Restore from a backup. # Configuration !prefix - Change the command prefix. # Miscellaneous !help - Show a list of commands or details of the specified command. !ping - Pong! !info - Show bot information. !serverinfo - Show server information. !channelinfo - Show channel information. !whois - Show user information. !welcome - Set up a welcome message. You can use %name% and %server% as placeholder. !say - Say something! !embed - Say an embedded message # Settings Go to https://antispambot.io/dashboard
Type '!help <command>' to show details.

Roles
?channel <#channel>
Set the active channel.
?message <message ID>
Set the active message.
?embed [Embed JSON]
Create an embed that will be used as the active message.
?normal <emoji> <role>
Give a role
?once <emoji> <role>
Setup a once role
?remove <emoji> <role>
Remove a role
?toggle <emoji> <role>
Setup a toggled role
?list
Show all roles.
